===Alternative spellings===
* [[voraphilia]], [[voreaphilia]] (probably by influence from the clipped form [[vore]])

===Etymology===
Latin [[voro|vorare]] "to devour" + [[-philia]].

===Noun===
'''vorarephilia'''
# A cannibalistic [[fetish]], chiefly practiced by [[role-playing]], involving the devouring of or being devoured by another person—whether live and whole ("soft vore"), or with gore or killing, and possible cooking as food ("hard vore").

